Hey, thank HEAVEN it’s snowball planting time again!

I know trending on the internets this week is Obama’s snowball.

But our Dogfather caught wind of Frenchie snowballs that were trending more than, well, that other guy OBAMA!!!

Guess what?

Here’s what Frackus and John Thomas came up with first:

The Snowball to end all Snowballs! The FreakSnowBall!

They really had never seen anything like it before. Ron doubted even Freud would have a chance to figure this one out.

And then Snooki Baby climbed it:

She’s a regular Anthony Weiner!

As you can see, Frackus gets into things pretty seriously. There’s a limit to how many nuggies 3 wives can give him.

And then, wouldn’t you know it, SNOW-BALL-FREAKIN-EATING-PRIZES just landed in our lap from The Popular Province of Busán in South Korea! We just knew we would LOVE Busan!!!

Unfortunately, we have no idea what they are.

We ate them, anyway. Muse dunno why this happened, I just know I had no clue what I have been doing.
